  "title": "Reciprocals of Cauchy Sequences",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $(x_n)$ be a Cauchy real sequence. If there exist $c>0$ and\n$N_0\\in\\mathbb{N}$ such that $|x_n|\\ge c$ for every $n\\ge N_0$, then\n$(1/x_n)$ is Cauchy.",
